sentences.en: When Lawrence H. Summers, the president of Harvard, suggested recently that one factor in women’s lagging progress in science and mathematics might be innate differences between the sexes, his comment Elicit ed so many fierce reactions that he quickly apologized.

sentences.en: In a statement, the fisheries department said: "DFO takes the protection, conservation and recovery of endangered species very seriously, and will continue to investigate the deaths of North Atlantic Right whales in the southern Gulf of St. Lawrence."

sentences.en: Other Santas, like Lawrence Jefferson, travel for a number of weeks near the holidays to play Jolly Ole Saint Nick. Better known as Santa Larry, Jefferson works at Minnesota’s Mall of America in the two weeks leading up to Christmas.
sentences.vi: Các ông già Noel khác, như Lawrence Jefferson, đi du lịch trong một số tuần gần những ngày nghỉ lễ để vào vai ông già Noel Nick. Được biết đến với tên gọi ông già Noel Larry, Jefferson làm việc tại Mall of America của Minnesota trong hai tuần lễ chào mừng Giáng sinh.

sentences.en: Scientists have the grisly task of picking through the huge decaying bodies of North Atlantic right whales after they were found floating in the mouth of Canada's Gulf of St Lawrence.
